page_0:
"Spirit Fire plays an important part in many of our purification rituals. Since its blue flames only burn negative spiritual energy, we use it to cleanse our dead.

If a Spirit Fire has been burning for a long time it can sometimes form crystals. These crystals are very fragile and burst into an ethereal cloud upon the slightest impact. We believe these clouds have similar effects as the fire itself, though without practical application we cannot go beyond speculation."

page_1:
"[there's a hastily scribbled note on the back:]

I discovered that members of the Dark Watch and any undead attack their own when they are hit directly by a crystal. This might be our only chance to calm the Necrop"